                            <comment id="98848" author="yujian" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 02:22:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The same failure also occurred on SLES11SP3/x86_64 client + RHEL6.5/x86_64 server test session:&lt;br/&gt;
